import './About.css'; import { useEffect } from 'react' import CV from '../../assets/CV.pdf' export const About = () => { useEffect(() => { let timer = setTimeout(function () { let lis = document.getElementById('perc-graphic').getElementsByTagName('li'); for (const e of lis) { let percentage = e.getElementsByClassName('percentage')[0]; let level = e.getElementsByClassName('language-lvl')[0].clientWidth; let container = e.getElementsByClassName('language-item')[0].clientWidth; let realPerc = ((level / container) * 100); percentage.innerHTML = Math.round(realPerc).toString() + '%'; } }, 4100) return () => clearTimeout(timer); } , []) return (

Software Engineer.

I'm Alex Sanchez a 24 yo. programmer originally hailing from Spain.


Actually focused in web solutions, as a full-stack developer. I have spent the last years learning from some branches of computer science and, especially, in software development, not just as a programmer but a graduate engineer.


Despite not having a long career, I work hard and assertively with my colleagues to offer a satisfactory and dynamic solution.


If you want to know more, check out my resume

Communicative

I tend to have a good and assertive communication with colleagues and clients.

Intuitive

Easy to use and intuitive UX/UI.

Dynamic

Websites don't need to be static. Making web pages dynamic makes them look more original and interactive.

Responsive

Being able to look right on every device is a must nowadays.

Skills

  • HTML
  • CSS
  • Javascript
  • SQL
  • C#
  • React
  • Node (Express)
  • Golang
  • Vue
  • C++
  • C
  • Microsoft Azure
  • Java
  • Python
  • Docker
  • MongoDB
); }
